Name: DarkFairyTales SleepingBeauty
About the game: DarkFairyTales SleepingBeauty is a jigsaw puzzle game. Gameplay Guide Victory Condition: You need to finish the jigsaw puzzle. How to Play: Left click to check one part, and left click change with another part. Function Keys Keyboard P: One key finish Keyboard S: Emergency avoidance (the background image turns white and you can continue to play) Keyboard N: Next level Game Features Pleasing Pictures Soothing Music
